&lt;h3 style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot; align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;Summary&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;This course will qualify those who successfully complete it to use the table saw, the mitre saw, and one or both bandsaws. It will comprise a half-hour classroom session covering safety and cleanliness guidelines and will be followed by a two to four-hour hands on session. During this session, using the tools will be demonstrated, with student use incorporated along with the demonstration. Part of this session will involve the student creating a small project from rough lumber.&lt;/p&gt;
